== Overview ==
The colossal Tribolt reactor is an experimental device that merges three [[Hydron Core|Hydron Reactors]] into one. There isn't actually a sane reason to ever use one of these.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Tribolt Hydron Reactor can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.

